She's not here.

45
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:06,600
Why are you here?

46
00:03:07,479 --> 00:03:08,320
Just last one time?

47
00:03:08,679 --> 00:03:10,119
Our history went way back than that.

48
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:13,919
But I don't know you.

49
