Shoo shoo.

50
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,039
Calm down.

51
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,679
Unless you're worried that
I know your secret

52
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:20,279
and I'm here to settle the score.

53
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,360
What secret?

54
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,039
